'''400100500260026''' was an area of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] in the [[Gordian Reach/Legends|Gordian Reach]] consisting of sixteen [[Planet/Legends|planets]] ruled by [[G0-T0 infrastructure planning system|G0-T0]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. In [[3946 BBY]], a number of G0-T0 droids seceded from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], cutting off [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] communications and blocking all traffic in and out of the [[Sector/Legends|sector]]. That same year, [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Tol Cressa]] organized a [[Liberation of 400100500260026|successful Republic effort]] to recapture the worlds.

